<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-3323] Python library does not handle escaped forward slash (&quot;/&quot;) in JSON</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3323</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As per json.org - a slash (&quot;/&quot;) may be escaped too.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When parsing a JSON that has escaped slashes, the Python library throws an exception as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Traceback (most recent call last):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  File &quot;lib/crawldata.py&quot;, line 32, in _&lt;em&gt;init&lt;/em&gt;_&lt;br/&gt;
    deserialize(base=self, buf=thrift_buf, protocol_factory=CrawlDataTJSONProtocolFactory())&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  File &quot;/usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/thrift/TSerialization.py&quot;, line 37, in deserialize&lt;br/&gt;
    base.read(protocol)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  File &quot;models/thrift/crawldata/ttypes.py&quot;, line 761, in read&lt;br/&gt;
    self.data.read(iprot)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  File &quot;models/thrift/crawldata/ttypes.py&quot;, line 241, in read&lt;br/&gt;
    _val19 = iprot.readString();&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  File &quot;/usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/thrift/protocol/TJSONProtocol.py&quot;, line 390, in readString&lt;br/&gt;
    return self.readJSONString(False)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  File &quot;/usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/thrift/protocol/TJSONProtocol.py&quot;, line 235, in readJSONString&lt;br/&gt;
    &quot;Expected control char&quot;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;TProtocolException: Expected control char&lt;/p&gt;</description>
